messages.content: Hi, thank you for calling Vacation Village Resorts. This is Jamie, a virtual agent on a recorded line. How can I help you today?
Payment.
Alright, I can help with your payment. Are you looking to pay your annual maintenance fees or your mortgage? Just to clarify, are you looking to pay your mortgage or your yearly
maintenance fees?
Maintenance.
Okay, I was able to pull up a matching record using your phone number. Can you tell me your first and last name?
Bernard Dolan.
Thanks, Bernard Dolan. Can you tell me what state you currently reside in?
Pennsylvania.
Great, your information is verified. Go ahead and let me know what you need help with regarding your maintenance payment.
Supposed to be an automatic withdrawal, but it has not come out yet.
Is it going to come out?
I see, you were expecting your maintenance fee to be withdrawn automatically but it hasn't come out yet. Can you confirm which
property this is for?
Account number. Eight seven seven two zero zero three three
four zero three zero.
Thanks for sharing your account number. Can you confirm the name of the resort or property this contract is for?
Vacation Village at Williamsburg.
So, for Vacation Village at Williamsburg, contract number eight seven seven two zero zero three three four zero three
zero, you want to know if your maintenance fee will be withdrawn automatically since it hasn't come out yet?
